## Page wrapper anatomy

```
udc-<id>-page (FRAME, 2800w, hug height, fill: surface-subtle)
Ōö£ŌöĆŌöĆ content (FRAME, FILL w, hug h, autolayout V, gap: space/1000, padding: space/800)
Ōöé   Ōö£ŌöĆŌöĆ HEADER          (dark card)
Ōöé   Ōö£ŌöĆŌöĆ ANATOMY         (light card)  ŌåÉ optional, omit for placeholder pages
Ōöé   Ōö£ŌöĆŌöĆ VARIANTS        (light card)  ŌåÉ omit if no inspectable component sets
Ōöé   Ōö£ŌöĆŌöĆ SUB-COMPONENTS  (light card)  ŌåÉ omit if no underscored components
Ōöé   Ōö£ŌöĆŌöĆ USAGE           (light card)
